Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡 你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,破坏墙壁的… 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.12,0:02:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.83,0:03:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让你再受伤害了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,居然破坏墙壁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道自己在做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.11,0:03:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为知道 所以不得不做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.62,0:03:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这是… 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是世界真正的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,除了墙内 全都毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,而宿命点不只是12只
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,会无数地来袭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是这个世界 还是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,都没有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要重复满开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.52,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,丧失身体功能也要继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天 连重要的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,开心的岁月的记忆也要失去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,遍体鳞伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.93,0:04:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,也要继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要再让重要的朋友成为牺牲品了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,为了不再成为勇者这一祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.91,0:04:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这个办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等… 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛 为什么要阻止我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是大赦的勇者…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,大赦明明隐瞒了真相 把你当作道具使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.59,0:05:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,道具…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.23,0:05:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈和勇者部的大家受伤的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不想再看了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友一次次受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经没法忍受了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,忍受不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,东… 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.37,0:05:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 暂时撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡 在哭…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡那么烦恼 那么痛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在旁边眼睁睁看着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我肯定能做到些什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是最好的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.79,0:07:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友一次次受伤 失去重要之人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经没法忍受了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,忍受不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.56,0:07:55.56,Text11a,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an2}警告\N因为勇者的精神状态不稳定\N无法生成与神树的灵力回路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,怎… 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,树…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.87,0:08:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要做到这个份上…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.49,0:08:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.57,0:08:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不知为何 突然想道谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不论是这个家 还是勇者部的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,都让姐姐一身扛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,树…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,而我总是又胆小 又弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,总是跟在姐姐后面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.42,0:09:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 其实我想和姐姐并肩前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,别说并肩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不知不觉间 你不是站在我前面了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.95,0:09:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,作为姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不能全靠妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没事了 树
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.97,0:09:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你真是我引以为豪的好妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 犬吠埼姐妹的女子力 就让它们见识一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们上 树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么没法变身！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.13,0:10:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这个朋友… 不合格…
Comment: 0,1:59:59.99,1:59:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友… 朋友没什么合格不合格的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在因为东乡的事情责备自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,该说像友奈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:11:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我想阻止她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我想阻止东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界毁灭掉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,就没法和大家在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,可是… 现在的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不要作为大赦的勇者战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,今后要作为勇者部的一员战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让我们的勇者部被破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不想看到友奈的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.77,0:12:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,再生后的家伙涌出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.46,0:13:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,先要歼灭那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,然后寻找东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,没有牺牲看来是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,诸行无常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 喂 现在开始才是重头戏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,远的给我听着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,近的就过来 也亲眼看着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.14,0:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是赞州中学二年级
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部部员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,三好夏凛的实力！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,来 收下吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.91,0:14:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部五条！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.59,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,其一！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,招呼要～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,打好！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.50,0:14:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部五条！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,其二！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量不放弃！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部五条！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.26,0:15:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,其三！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.04,0:15:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃好～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.53,0:15:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,睡好！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部五条！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,其四！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.91,0:15:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,烦恼要沟通！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,另一只呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 伤得太浅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者部五条！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,其五！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,车到山前多半～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有路！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,见识了吗 勇者部的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.66,0:16:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.64,0:16:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.93,0:17:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,夏凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,振作点！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.88,0:17:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.10,0:17:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 眼睛和耳朵好像都废掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是友奈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 是友奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吗 友奈 我的精彩表现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看到啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我都看到啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你好厉害 夏凛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这种… 这种事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,本想去找东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我有话想说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.09,0:18:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我长久以来一直在接受勇者的训练
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,只有战斗是我的存在价值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是个道具
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是… 多亏大家 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈的话 连东乡的心意也能改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.77,0:18:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,能救东乡的只有友奈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是最好的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你看到这个光景了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.85,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那应该明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再破坏墙壁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界 大赦的做法 勇者的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是多么悲惨的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要得到救赎 只有这个办法了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,就算如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.45,0:19:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我作为部长 作为前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,都要阻止你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,东乡！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,咬紧牙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 东乡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,安静一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 树
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,敌人停止进攻了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个 请让开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能让开！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:21:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 凭勇者的力量 没法伤害神树本体吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 带这个去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,一定能把神树…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.46,0:21:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没力气了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,树…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.52,0:21:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你想杀我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.18,0:21:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.58,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来 就能把大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,勇者～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.76,0:22:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 风前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.17,0:22:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,友奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.02,0:22:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不会迷惑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我来守护勇者部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.85,0:22:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,守护东乡！
